379
00:28:06,558 --> 00:28:08,204
- Hmm?

380
00:28:08,204 --> 00:28:09,939
- I called the station,

381
00:28:09,939 --> 00:28:12,381
there weren't any trains before noon.

382
00:28:12,381 --> 00:28:13,214
- Really?

383
00:28:14,207 --> 00:28:15,906
Well then I suppose poor Mr. Reynolds

384
00:28:15,906 --> 00:28:19,355
had a long wait after all didn't he?

385
00:28:19,355 --> 00:28:20,522
- So it seems.

386
00:28:21,438 --> 00:28:23,271
- Well, goodnight all.

387
00:28:28,496 --> 00:28:31,163
(ominous music)

388
