517
00:39:15,587 --> 00:39:18,623
Now this is much more in
keeping with the times,

518
00:39:18,623 --> 00:39:20,701
wouldn't you say?

519
00:39:20,701 --> 00:39:24,868
Medical, mechanical, a
certain scientific quality?

520
00:39:31,187 --> 00:39:33,664
Every society has an acceptable form

521
00:39:33,664 --> 00:39:35,983
for it's magic Mr. Delaney.

522
00:39:35,983 --> 00:39:39,130
Whether it's dead cats
and tree stump water

523
00:39:39,130 --> 00:39:42,973
or electrolitic catalisis
and radium treatments.

524
00:39:42,973 --> 00:39:45,890
(groaning in pain)

525
00:39:49,767 --> 00:39:52,512
